description:
&lt;p&gt;The StaffBank for the Elective Orthopaedic Centre is seeking enthusiastic Orthopaedic Anaesthetics nurses to work ad hoc and full time shifts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The EOC is an NHS treatment centre providing regional elective orthopaedic surgery services (including in-patient, day-case and outpatient). &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Established by the four South West London Acute Trusts to deliver strategic change in the delivery of planned orthopaedic care, the SWLEOC provides high quality, cost efficient, elective orthopaedic services amongst the best in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pay - £25.00-£30.00 per hour&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;StaffBank can offer you the flexibility you desire with the benefit of the NHS pension scheme, and more. Our jobs would bring a brilliant opportunity to anyone who is looking to top up their current salary, skills or to accommodate their personal circumstances. You’ll be reliable, dedicated and flexible, with a commitment to competent, high quality care delivery.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;StaffBank requires you to have: &lt;br /&gt;* Registration with the NMC &lt;br /&gt;* Eligibility to work within the UK &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;StaffBank can offer you:&lt;br /&gt;* Flexible hours&lt;br /&gt;* Free Mandatory training and annual updates&lt;br /&gt;* Support from a friendly and approachable team&lt;br /&gt;* Excellent, Competitive pay rates &lt;br /&gt;* Access to the NHS Pension&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of the recruitment process you will be required to complete an enhanced CRB check. We regret that we cannot accept applications from candidates seeking work permits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apply now to find out more about this incredible opportunity! Successful candidates will also have an opportunity to learn about our great benefits!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bank Partners are a leading provider of independent staffing bank management and outsourced staffing services providing workers to some of the largest trusts in the NHS. We have over 20 years experience in managing hospital banks and we take pride in the knowledge that we provide a high quality service to the trusts we represent, supplying them with workers across multiple specialism’s including Doctors, Nurses and Allied Health Professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
